name: CoronaryArteryBypassGraft
title: Coronary Artery Bypass Graft
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This value set contains concepts that represent coronary artery bypass graft procedures.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use the Quality Data Model (QDM) datatype related to Procedure, Performed.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes only relevant concepts associated with patients who have had a coronary artery bypass graft procedure.),(Exclusion Criteria: No exclusions.)
